whereas.text:
Whereas supporters of democracy worldwide recognize the
			 valor of the people of Ukraine in seeking to advance democratic governance in
			 their country;

Whereas the role of the Parliament of Ukraine, the
			 Verkhovna Rada, is essential to ensuring democratic governance and a balance of
			 power among the branches of the Government of Ukraine;

Whereas the people of the United States affirm the
			 positive role being played by the Parliament of Ukraine in averting a
			 constitutional crisis in that transitional republic;
